name: Dayle Haddon
summary: Canadian model and actress Dayle Haddon has passed away at the age of 76 due to suspected carbon monoxide poisoning. Haddon was found dead in Solebury Township, Bucks County, Pennsylvania, at the home of Hallmark actor Marc Blucas. Another individual was also injured in the incident. The investigation is ongoing, but authorities believe a carbon monoxide leak may have caused the tragic event. Haddon was known for her successful modeling career and her roles in films and television shows. Her death has been met with sadness and condolences from the entertainment industry and beyond.
